    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Description\n\nWhen setting up a repo with a `package.json5` file, tailwindcss server fails to detect root.\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/b6936cb85d1e95b5ff00016b1185ab1a14450579/lua/lspconfig/configs/tailwindcss.lua#L102-L115\n\n\nRoot cause is that we're checking for `package.json` (thus `package.json5` or `node_modules` won't suffice)\nhttps://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/b6936cb85d1e95b5ff00016b1185ab1a14450579/lua/lspconfig/util.lua#L119-L134\nEasiest fix off the top of my head is to check for both `package.json` and `packge.json5`\n\nBut I would like to hear what you guys think before I raise a PR for this.\n\nP.S. Much thanks for making neovim a nice place to live in",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
